node.text:
I visit the 9 bedroom Ultima chalet in Geneva, Switzerland, costing $100,000 to rent it out for a week, (including a transfers to and from Geneva airport, full breakfast, private chef, service, housekeeping twice a day, and all on site staff as well butler and driver) 😱

#ultima #ultimamegeve  #offwhite #moncler #baccarat #heronpreston #watches #watchanish #luxury #cars #automotive #alecmonopoly #art #watchporn #carporn #foodporn #horology #igtv #menswear #menwithclass #louisvuitton #gucci #mastermindjapan #luxurywatches #style #watchesofinstagram #dailywatch #lv #supreme

node.text:
🎁 Guys we are hosting an insane competition with @rebelliontimepieces this weekend, with 3 prizes to win! 

Me & @tomclaeren are going to race and you can vote for who you back to win on the Rebellion Timepieces Instagram page. 

We will randomly pick 3 winners among those who chose the correct Champion (I’m definitely better than Tom!)…and remember you must be following @rebelliontimepieces to enter.

Here are the prizes:

🥇1st prize : one Rebellion Timepiece Tour Auto Edition

🥈2nd prize: a pair of Sunglasses by Rebellion x Roland ItIen

🥉3rd prize :  2 VIP passes to a GT world challenge race with access to Rebellion VIP lounge 

The winners will be announced by Rebellion within 24h, good luck to you all !
